OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1774795970
OL,3,CWoman calls for ban on delivery apps
OL,4,Cselling alcohol after sister's death
OL,6,FA woman from Lincoln is calling for
OL,7,Ftougher restrictions on delivery apps
OL,8,Fafter discovering her late sister was
OL,9,Fspending up to #1,500 a month getting
OL,10,Falcohol delivered to her door.
OL,12,F35-year-old Zoe Hughes died in 2023
OL,13,Fand had struggled with alcoholism in
OL,14,Fthe years leading up to her death.
OL,16,FHer younger sister, Alexandria, says
OL,17,Fthe ease with which she could access
OL,18,Flarge amounts of alcohol through
OL,19,Fdelivery apps helped enable the
OL,20,Faddiction.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/6
