PN,36502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1774795970
OL,3,CWoman calls for ban on delivery apps
OL,4,Cselling alcohol after sister's death
OL,6,FZoe started drinking alcohol around
OL,7,F2019, which spiralled into addiction.
OL,9,FWhen she was found dead in her home
OL,10,Ffour years later, her family
OL,11,Fdiscovered how much she had been
OL,12,Fspending to get alcohol via delivery
OL,13,Fapps.
OL,15,FAlexandria believes there should be
OL,16,Ftougher restrictions and more
OL,17,Foversight.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,366,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1774795970
OL,3,CWoman calls for ban on delivery apps
OL,4,Cselling alcohol after sister's death
OL,6,F"It took her social life, she didn't
OL,7,Freally need to get ready for the day
OL,8,Fbecause she had nowhere to go because
OL,9,Fthe delivery apps were on standby to
OL,10,Fdeliver it to her. Eventually all that
OL,11,Fdid was isolate her to her home."
OL,13,F"For me personally, a shop opens at a
OL,14,Fcertain time and shuts at a certain
OL,15,Ftime, these delivery apps don't.
OL,16,FThey're not adhering to their policy.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,366,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1774795970
OL,3,CWoman calls for ban on delivery apps
OL,4,Cselling alcohol after sister's death
OL,6,F"There'd be times she was passed out
OL,7,Ffrom the alcohol and it was on her
OL,8,Fdoorstep, so nobody was really casting
OL,9,Fan eye over her to make that judgement
OL,10,Fof should she be served, or should she
OL,11,Fnot."
OL,13,FThe three major food delivery apps,
OL,14,FDeliveroo, Uber Eats, and Just Eat all
OL,15,Fsaid the welfare of customers "is
OL,16,Fextremely important" and have policies
OL,17,Fin place to meet their legal
OL,18,Fresponsibilities.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
