FL,366,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1774795970
OL,3,CWoman calls for ban on delivery apps
OL,4,Cselling alcohol after sister's death
OL,6,FDeliveroo said it has a "specialist
OL,7,Fpolicy to suspend or delete a
OL,8,Fcustomer's account, working with
OL,9,Ffriends or family if they report a
OL,10,Fwelfare concern to us."
OL,12,FUber Eats said it has an "ongoing
OL,13,Fpartnership with Drinkaware to
OL,14,Fimplement further alcohol safety
OL,15,Fmeasures, including clear signposting
OL,16,Fto support resources and the ability
OL,17,Fto restrict platform access for
OL,18,Fcustomers where necessary."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
